title: Donington 1988 Monsters of Rock - Iron Maiden - KISS - Dave Lee
description:
1988 Donington Monsters of Rock Special featuring interviews with all the bands and includes an early interview with Axl Rose. Presented by the Bailey Brothers who also do the interviews. Only partial live performance by Iron Maiden shown all others are music videos. Sorry for the quality as this is ripped from a 20 year old video tape.

Bands featured
Helloween
Guns n Roses
Megadeth
Dave Lee Roth
KISS
Iron Maiden

Video=VHS, Audio=Mono, Duration=1h 53m 40s
